data.description: Welcome to the desirable and well-established Brandon Woods Community! Located in the heart of Florence. Definitely Will Not Last Long! This home features a nice porch, 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, lvt flooring, and so much more. The kitchen has ceramic tile flooring and is equipped with stainless steel appliances to include the refrigerator, dishwasher,microwave,and stove. The fenced backyard is perfect for entertaining friends and family. Also has 2 nice storage buildings. Don't miss your opportunity to own this beautiful home.
